// Man page for rnet
manRnet="RNET(1)                          X Shell Manual                          RNET(1)

<b>NAME</b>
    rnet - Refresh network interface
<b>SYNOPSIS</b>
    <b>rnet</b>
<b>DESCRIPTION</b>
    Refresh and reinitialize the network interface.
<b>EXAMPLE:</b>
    <b>rnet</b>
    Refresh network interface
<b>SEE ALSO</b>
    <b>active</b>, <b>ifconfig</b>, <b>iwconfig</b>"